    "original_content": "<h3>Development Progress</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Jamal working on live-coded landing page for <a href=\"http://dehumanapi.com\">dehumanapi.com</a></li>\n<li>End-to-end test simulation for app click upload flow nearly complete\n<ul>\n<li>May need to switch from REST to JSON IPC if necessary</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Mobile app designs finalized for script representation\n<ul>\n<li>Explored multiple options to improve script readability on mobile</li>\n<li>Clear direction established for future mobile app development</li>\n<li>Loom video walkthrough to be shared with app team</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Data Acquisition &amp; Licensing</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Email outreach continuing with listen notes scraping</li>\n<li>Strong response rate: targeting 2k hours within 1-2 days</li>\n<li>Pricing settled at $25-30 per hour for most prospects</li>\n<li>Potential exclusive deal: 3.2k hours from podcaster with two shows\n<ul>\n<li>2000 hours + 1200 hours</li>\n<li>Exclusive AI training license</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>MLG Sample Analysis</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial samples analyzed show consistent technical specs\n<ul>\n<li>Frequency range: 0-20 kilohertz across all samples</li>\n<li>Bitrate consistent throughout dataset</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Evaluation code likely broken based on multi-sample analysis</li>\n<li>Spanish samples require review (24-bit, 48kHz requirements)\n<ul>\n<li>Higher quality requirements than English samples</li>\n<li>Fewer samples available but need approval for recording this week</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Next Steps</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Vedant: Provide logo and basic assets for UGC video creation</li>\n<li>Adithya: Complete MLG sample analysis for Spanish content and update tracking sheet</li>\n<li>Julian: Share notes from yesterday’s recording sessions and fix evaluation checks</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<p>Chat with meeting transcript: <a href=\"https://notes.granola.ai/t/8a248885-2e2c-45f6-bcce-ab7d8564d923\">https://notes.granola.ai/t/8a248885-2e2c-45f6-bcce-ab7d8564d923</a></p>\n",
